This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) as it presents a new corpus annotated with preposition supersenses, which is a topic related to natural language processing. It could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) as the annotation process likely involved some form of automated classification. Additionally, the paper may fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with improving semantic understanding in language. Information retrieval (cs.IR) could also be a relevant sub-category as the annotated corpus could be used for information extraction tasks. Finally, cybernetics (cs.CY) could be a possible sub-category as the paper deals with organizing and categorizing language data.
